name: relax
description: At present, the role of AI machine for Human is to do housework and work. Especially after playing the game Detroit: Become Human, I feel uncomfortable and have been used by the master.What I want to express in this work is that robots can also have a comfortable time to enjoy. Taking a bath is undoubtedly a relaxing moment for human beings, so I choose this scene.(1920 * 1440)
